Findings were written to [publicmenu-260321-132753-codex-findings.md](C:/Dev/menuapp-code-review/pipeline/chain-state/publicmenu-260321-132753-codex-findings.md). I documented 9 findings total: 6 P1, 2 P2, 1 P3. The main issues are the old inline table-verification flow still being present in `CartView`, the new bottom sheet hardcoding 4-digit codes and lacking an explicit confirm CTA, partner lookup masking backend failures as “not found”, restore logic in `useTableSession` never retrying after transient failure, and pickup/delivery checkout still dropping loyalty UI.

